{"tid":307374,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] HSBC海外提款一問","createTime":"2017-07-03T10:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T13:30:48.000Z","uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf77a38e00fbce9548d6e8895633abf0040483d0","tid":307374,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"想問下去HSBC ATM開通完海外提款之後<br />\n仲有冇其他野要搞?<br />\n<br />\n我打算去英國既...<br />\n想問下係咪去到英國HSBC ATM<br />\n用返香港張銀行卡就搞掂?<br />\n然後手續費就每次200蚊HKD<br />\n匯率就計返當日HSBC既匯率<br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n有上網同去櫃台問<br />\n但好怕到時有咩野出錯<br />\n就會拎唔到錢冇錢用<br />\n所以想上黎問下人有冇試過海外提款 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e247560d541d01f41ebe79ab1fe3d8e8574d45c1","tid":307374,"uid":11642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:13:30.000Z","msg":"好似係20蚊"},{"pid":"9055449f28a908b78aa67249978219963ed5e740","tid":307374,"uid":7225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"你張卡有無銀聯？<br />\n有就有銀聯嘅機都㩒到。"},{"pid":"dd7101db26d4d46f2458f7d2321018213122c2d5","tid":307374,"uid":34522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:22:28.000Z","msg":"最好就去番hsbc櫃員機禁，歐洲唔係部部櫃員機都支援晶片提款卡，一部唔得就試第部"},{"pid":"a829d38d1e4c75c3a9678be6e281fc9aefb8b4e4","tid":307374,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你張卡有無銀聯？<br />\n有就有銀聯嘅機都㩒到。</blockquote><br />\n有銀聯呀 <br />\n唔該 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e69225e4a6757799377ad47a461c6184b5bb48","tid":307374,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好就去番hsbc櫃員機禁，歐洲唔係部部櫃員機都支援晶片提款卡，一部唔得就試第部</blockquote><br />\n收到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140a951317ba773d0656ed78724fd75134c22f25","tid":307374,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似係20蚊</blockquote><br />\n係喎 我睇返 係20蚊<br />\n我記錯左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24344d8a4f5b813d2c6121a81696b29a51e5e03a","tid":307374,"uid":561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:30:58.000Z","msg":"$20<br />\n跟銀聯rate"},{"pid":"749cc7a089d0194a7e11cdee3efc79790d935f8f","tid":307374,"uid":93973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:30:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>$20<br />\n跟銀聯rate</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果用香港HSBC 銀聯 ATM卡就跟 銀聯rate；<br />\n如果用香港HSBC PLUS ATM卡，會用邊個匯率？<br />\n有人話跟Visa，有話跟HSBC 電匯價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}